description: Number of nonisomorphic circulant oriented graphs (i.e. Cayley graphs for the cyclic group) of order n.
comments: These and subsequent values for (twice) squarefree and (twice) prime-squared orders can be found in the Liskovets reference.
links: V. A. Liskovets, Some identities for enumerators of circulant graphs.
author: _Valery A. Liskovets_, May 09 2001
